<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>애슐리퀸즈 고객여정지도 2026 | CX팀</title>
<style>
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;500;700;900&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap');

:root {
  --navy:    #1E2761;
  --navy-light: #2D3A80;
  --white:   #FFFFFF;
  --bg:      #F4F5F9;
  --card:    #FFFFFF;
  --red:     #C0392B;
  --red-bg:  #FDECEA;
  --red-mid: #E57373;
  --amber:   #D17000;
  --amber-bg:#FFF3E0;
  --amber-mid:#FFB74D;
  --green:   #1B6B3A;
  --green-bg:#E8F5E9;
  --green-mid:#66BB6A;
  --blue-acc:#4F6FD4;
  --gray-50: #F8F9FC;
  --gray-100:#EEF0F5;
  --gray-300:#CBD0DC;
  --gray-500:#7B8299;
  --gray-700:#3D4460;
  --border:  rgba(30,39,97,0.10);
  --shadow:  0 2px 12px rgba(30,39,97,0.08);
  --shadow-lg: 0 6px 28px rgba(30,39,97,0.13);
}

* { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

body {
  font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
  background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--gray-700);
  line-height: 1.6;
}

/* ─── HEADER ─────────────────────────────────── */
.site-header {
  background: var(--navy);
  padding: 0;
  position: sticky;
  top: 0;
  z-index: 100;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.18);
}
.header-inner {
  max-width: 1280px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 14px 32px;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
}
.header-brand { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1px; }
.header-brand .brand-main {
  font-size: 18px; font-weight: 900; color: #fff; letter-spacing: -0.3px;
}
.header-brand .brand-sub {
  font-size: 11px; color: #8BAAF5; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}
.header-meta {
  display: flex; gap: 20px; align-items: center;
}
.meta-pill {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
  border-radius: 20px;
  padding: 4px 14px;
  font-size: 11px; color: #B0BEE8; font-weight: 500;
}
.meta-pill strong { color: #fff; }

/* ─── HERO STRIP ──────────────────────────────── */
.hero {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy) 0%, #2D3A80 60%, #3B4FA0 100%);
  padding: 40px 32px 36px;
  text-align: center;
}
.hero-kicker {
  display: inline-block;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.22);
  border-radius: 20px;
  padding: 4px 16px;
  font-size: 11px; color: #8BAAF5; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 1px;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}
.hero h1 {
  font-size: 38px; font-weight: 900; color: #fff;
  letter-spacing: -1px; margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.hero-desc { font-size: 13px; color: #B0BEE8; margin-bottom: 28px; }
.hero-stats {
  display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 20px; flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.hero-stat {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 12px 24px; text-align: center; min-width: 120px;
}
.hero-stat .sv { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 900; color: #fff; letter-spacing: -0.5px; }
.hero-stat .sl { font-size: 10px; color: #8BAAF5; margin-top: 2px; font-weight: 500; }

/* ─── CONTENT WRAPPER ─────────────────────────── */
.content {
  max-width: 1280px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 32px 24px 64px;
}

/* ─── SECTION TITLE ───────────────────────────── */
.sec-title {
  font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gray-500);
  text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  margin-bottom: 14px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
}
.sec-title::before {
  content: ''; display: block;
  width: 18px; height: 3px; background: var(--navy); border-radius: 2px;
}

/* ─── PHASE + JOURNEY ROW ─────────────────────── */
.journey-block { margin-bottom: 36px; }

.phase-row {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 2fr 5fr 2fr;
  gap: 6px;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.phase-pill {
  text-align: center; padding: 6px 0; border-radius: 8px;
  font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700;
}
.phase-pill.pre  { background: #B5D4F4; color: #042C53; }
.phase-pill.dur  { background: #CECBF6; color: #26215C; }
.phase-pill.post { background: #9FE1CB; color: #04342C; }

.stage-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(9, 1fr);
  gap: 6px;
}

.stage-card {
  background: var(--card);
  border-radius: 10px;
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  padding: 12px 6px 10px;
  text-align: center;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.stage-card::before {
  content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 4px;
}
.stage-card.ok::before   { background: var(--green-mid); }
.stage-card.warn::before { background: var(--amber-mid); }
.stage-card.crit::before { background: var(--red-mid); }

.stage-card:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg); }

.stage-icon { font-size: 22px; margin-bottom: 6px; }
.stage-name { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gray-700); margin-bottom: 4px; line-height: 1.3; }
.stage-sub  { font-size: 8.5px; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 6px; }
.stage-card.ok   .stage-sub { color: var(--green); }
.stage-card.warn .stage-sub { color: var(--amber); }
.stage-card.crit .stage-sub { color: var(--red); }
.stage-pct { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 900; }
.stage-card.ok   .stage-pct { color: var(--green); }
.stage-card.warn .stage-pct { color: var(--amber); }
.stage-card.crit .stage-pct { color: var(--red); }
.stage-badge {
  position: absolute; top: 8px; right: 6px;
  font-size: 7.5px; font-weight: 700; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid;
}
.stage-card.ok   .stage-badge { background: var(--green-bg); color: var(--green); border-color: var(--green-mid); }
.stage-card.warn .stage-badge { background: var(--amber-bg); color: var(--amber); border-color: var(--amber-mid); }
.stage-card.crit .stage-badge { background: var(--red-bg);   color: var(--red);   border-color: var(--red-mid);   }

/* ─── EMOTION CURVE ───────────────────────────── */
.curve-wrap {
  background: var(--card); border-radius: 12px;
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  padding: 20px 24px;
  margin-bottom: 28px;
  box-shadow: var(--shadow);
}

/* ─── METRIC BARS ─────────────────────────────── */
.metric-grid {
  display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(9, 1fr); gap: 6px;
  margin-bottom: 28px;
}
.metric-card {
  background: var(--card); border-radius: 10px;
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  padding: 10px 6px; text-align: center;
  box-shadow: var(--shadow);
}
.metric-card.crit { border-color: var(--red-mid); background: var(--red-bg); }
.metric-card.warn { border-color: var(--amber-mid); }
.mc-val { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 900; }
.metric-card.ok   .mc-val { color: var(--green); }
.metric-card.warn .mc-val { color: var(--amber); }
.metric-card.crit .mc-val { color: var(--red); }
.mc-bar-track { height: 5px; background: var(--gray-100); border-radius: 3px; margin: 5px 4px 4px; }
.mc-bar-fill  { height: 5px; border-radius: 3px; }
.mc-lbl { font-size: 9px; color: var(--gray-500); font-weight: 500; }

/* ─── TWO-COL DETAIL CARDS ────────────────────── */
.detail-section { margin-bottom: 28px; }
.detail-section-header {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 14px;
}
.ds-badge {
  font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; padding: 3px 12px;
  border-radius: 20px; border: 1.5px solid;
}
.ds-badge.crit { background: var(--red-bg);   color: var(--red);   border-color: var(--red);   }
.ds-badge.warn { background: var(--amber-bg); color: var(--amber); border-color: var(--amber); }
.ds-title { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 900; color: var(--navy); }

.detail-grid-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 14px; }
.detail-grid-4 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 12px; }

.dcard {
  background: var(--card); border-radius: 12px;
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  overflow: hidden; box-shadow: var(--shadow);
}
.dcard-head {
  padding: 14px 16px 10px;
  display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start;
}
.dcard-head.crit { border-left: 4px solid var(--red); }
.dcard-head.warn { border-left: 4px solid var(--amber); }
.dcard-title { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--navy); }
.dcard-pct { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 900; }
.dcard-head.crit .dcard-pct { color: var(--red); }
.dcard-head.warn .dcard-pct { color: var(--amber); }
.dcard-divider { height: 1px; background: var(--gray-100); margin: 0 16px; }
.dcard-body { padding: 12px 16px; }
.dcard-items { list-style: none; margin-bottom: 14px; }
.dcard-items li {
  font-size: 11px; color: var(--gray-700); padding: 4px 0;
  display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 8px; line-height: 1.5;
}
.dcard-items li::before {
  content: ''; flex-shrink: 0;
  width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%; margin-top: 5px;
}
.dcard.crit .dcard-items li::before { background: var(--red-mid); }
.dcard.warn .dcard-items li::before { background: var(--amber-mid); }

.voc-label { font-size: 9.5px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gray-500); margin-bottom: 6px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.8px; }
.voc-quote {
  font-size: 10.5px; font-style: italic; line-height: 1.65;
  padding: 9px 12px; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.dcard.crit .voc-quote { background: var(--red-bg); color: #7B1A1A; border-left: 2px solid var(--red-mid); }
.dcard.warn .voc-quote { background: var(--amber-bg); color: #7B5200; border-left: 2px solid var(--amber-mid); }

/* ─── PRIORITY ────────────────────────────────── */
.priority-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 12px; }
.p-card {
  background: var(--card); border-radius: 12px;
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  padding: 16px 18px; box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  display: flex; gap: 14px; align-items: flex-start;
}
.p-badge {
  flex-shrink: 0; width: 36px; height: 36px;
  border-radius: 8px; border: 1.5px solid;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-size: 11px; font-weight: 900;
}
.p-badge.p1 { background: var(--red-bg);   color: var(--red);   border-color: var(--red); }
.p-badge.p2 { background: var(--amber-bg); color: var(--amber); border-color: var(--amber); }
.p-badge.p3 { background: #E8EEFF;         color: var(--blue-acc); border-color: var(--blue-acc); }
.p-content {}
.p-title { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 4px; }
.p-detail { font-size: 11px; color: var(--gray-500); line-height: 1.55; }

/* ─── MODAL ────────────────────────────────────── */
.overlay {
  display: none; position: fixed; inset: 0;
  background: rgba(10,15,40,0.45); z-index: 500;
  align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 20px;
}
.overlay.on { display: flex; }
.modal {
  background: var(--card); border-radius: 16px;
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  width: min(560px, 100%); max-height: 85vh; overflow-y: auto;
  box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(10,15,40,0.25);
  animation: popIn 0.18s ease;
}
@keyframes popIn {
  from { transform: scale(0.94) translateY(8px); opacity: 0; }
  to   { transform: scale(1)    translateY(0);   opacity: 1; }
}
.modal-top {
  padding: 18px 20px 14px;
  display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-100);
  position: sticky; top: 0; background: var(--card); z-index: 1;
  border-radius: 16px 16px 0 0;
}
.modal-title { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--navy); }
.modal-close {
  background: var(--gray-100); border: none; cursor: pointer;
  width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%; font-size: 14px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  color: var(--gray-500); transition: background 0.1s;
}
.modal-close:hover { background: var(--gray-300); }
.modal-body { padding: 18px 20px; }
.modal-cols { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 14px; }
.modal-col h4 { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gray-500); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.8px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.modal-q {
  font-size: 11.5px; line-height: 1.65; color: var(--gray-700);
  background: var(--gray-50); border-radius: 8px; padding: 9px 11px;
  margin-bottom: 7px;
}
.modal-q.neg { border-left: 3px solid var(--red-mid); }
.modal-q.pos { border-left: 3px solid var(--green-mid); }

/* ─── FOOTER ───────────────────────────────────── */
.site-footer {
  background: var(--navy); color: #8BAAF5;
  text-align: center; padding: 20px;
  font-size: 11px;
}

/* ─── LEGEND ────────────────────────────────────── */
.legend-row {
  display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap;
  margin-top: 12px;
}
.legend-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; font-size: 10px; color: var(--gray-500); }
.legend-dot { width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- HEADER -->
<header class="site-header">
  <div class="header-inner">
    <div class="header-brand">
      <span class="brand-main">애슐리퀸즈 고객여정지도</span>
      <span class="brand-sub">CX팀 VOC 분석 리포트 · 2026.04.27</span>
    </div>
    <div class="header-meta">
      <div class="meta-pill">리뷰 <strong>24,692건</strong></div>
      <div class="meta-pill">평균 <strong>4.57점</strong></div>
      <div class="meta-pill">저평점 <strong>3.6%</strong></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-kicker">Customer Journey Map</div>
  <h1>고객여정 VOC 분석</h1>
  <p class="hero-desc">예약부터 퇴점까지 9개 단계 · 저평점(1–2점) 894건 불만 패턴 기반</p>
  <div class="hero-stats">
    <div class="hero-stat"><div class="sv">34.7%</div><div class="sl">최고 불만 구간 · 식사</div></div>
    <div class="hero-stat"><div class="sv">32.1%</div><div class="sl">2위 불만 구간 · 샐러드바</div></div>
    <div class="hero-stat"><div class="sv">121건</div><div class="sl">짜다 단일 키워드</div></div>
    <div class="hero-stat"><div class="sv">58건</div><div class="sl">샐러드바 비어있음</div></div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="content">

  <!-- ① JOURNEY MAP -->
  <div class="journey-block">
    <div class="sec-title">고객여정 한눈에 보기</div>

    <div class="phase-row">
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:6px;">
        <div class="phase-pill pre">방문 전</div>
        <div class="phase-pill pre">방문 전</div>
      </div>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(5,1fr);gap:6px;">
        <div class="phase-pill dur">방문 중</div>
        <div class="phase-pill dur">방문 중</div>
        <div class="phase-pill dur">방문 중</div>
        <div class="phase-pill dur">방문 중</div>
        <div class="phase-pill dur">방문 중</div>
      </div>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:6px;">
        <div class="phase-pill post">방문 후</div>
        <div class="phase-pill post">방문 후</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="stage-grid" id="stageGrid">
      <div class="stage-card ok"   onclick="openModal(0)"><span class="stage-badge">양호</span><div class="stage-icon">📅</div><div class="stage-name">예약</div><div class="stage-sub">–</div><div class="stage-pct">6.9%</div></div>
      <div class="stage-card warn" onclick="openModal(1)"><span class="stage-badge">주의</span><div class="stage-icon">💳</div><div class="stage-name">선결제</div><div class="stage-sub">–</div><div class="stage-pct">2.6%</div></div>
      <div class="stage-card warn" onclick="openModal(2)"><span class="stage-badge">주의</span><div class="stage-icon">🪑</div><div class="stage-name">테이블 착석</div><div class="stage-sub">–</div><div class="stage-pct">21%</div></div>
      <div class="stage-card crit" onclick="openModal(3)"><span class="stage-badge">위험</span><div class="stage-icon">🥗</div><div class="stage-name">샐러드바</div><div class="stage-sub">음식없음</div><div class="stage-pct">32.1%</div></div>
      <div class="stage-card crit" onclick="openModal(4)"><span class="stage-badge">위험</span><div class="stage-icon">🍽</div><div class="stage-name">식사</div><div class="stage-sub">맛·품질·청결</div><div class="stage-pct">34.7%</div></div>
      <div class="stage-card warn" onclick="openModal(5)"><span class="stage-badge">주의</span><div class="stage-icon">🤖</div><div class="stage-name">버싱로봇</div><div class="stage-sub">셀프클린</div><div class="stage-pct">8.2%</div></div>
      <div class="stage-card warn" onclick="openModal(6)"><span class="stage-badge">주의</span><div class="stage-icon">⏱</div><div class="stage-name">100분제</div><div class="stage-sub">–</div><div class="stage-pct">16%</div></div>
      <div class="stage-card ok"   onclick="openModal(7)"><span class="stage-badge">양호</span><div class="stage-icon">🚗</div><div class="stage-name">주차</div><div class="stage-sub">–</div><div class="stage-pct">1.3%</div></div>
      <div class="stage-card ok"   onclick="openModal(8)"><span class="stage-badge">양호</span><div class="stage-icon">🚪</div><div class="stage-name">퇴점</div><div class="stage-sub">–</div><div class="stage-pct">4.0%</div></div>
    </div>

    <div class="legend-row">
      <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:var(--red-mid)"></div>위험 (>25%)</div>
      <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:var(--amber-mid)"></div>주의 (10–25%)</div>
      <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:var(--green-mid)"></div>양호 (<10%)</div>
      <span style="font-size:10px;color:var(--gray-500);margin-left:auto;">※ 카드 클릭 → 실제 VOC 확인 · 불만 언급률: 저평점 리뷰(1–2점) 중 해당 단계 언급 비율</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ② EMOTION CURVE -->
  <div class="curve-wrap">
    <div class="sec-title" style="margin-bottom:10px;">고객 감정 흐름</div>
    <svg width="100%" viewBox="0 0 900 110" role="img" aria-label="고객 감정 흐름 곡선">
      <defs>
        <linearGradient id="curveFill" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
          <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#4F6FD4" stop-opacity="0.2"/>
          <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#4F6FD4" stop-opacity="0.01"/>
        </linearGradient>
      </defs>
      <!-- Grid -->
      <line x1="30" y1="15" x2="30" y2="88" stroke="#CBD0DC" stroke-width="0.5"/>
      <line x1="30" y1="88" x2="880" y2="88" stroke="#CBD0DC" stroke-width="0.5"/>
      <text x="24" y="18" font-size="9" fill="#1B6B3A" text-anchor="end" font-weight="700">만족</text>
      <text x="24" y="91" font-size="9" fill="#C0392B" text-anchor="end" font-weight="700">불만</text>
      <!-- Stage labels -->
      <text x="80"  y="104" font-size="8.5" fill="#7B8299" text-anchor="middle">예약</text>
      <text x="180" y="104" font-size="8.5" fill="#7B8299" text-anchor="middle">선결제</text>
      <text x="280" y="104" font-size="8.5" fill="#7B8299" text-anchor="middle">착석</text>
